The paper deals with image matching and feature detection, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The application domain is book cover identification, which suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as relevant sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning (cs.DL) for feature extraction, and the evaluation of different methods in terms of accuracy and speed, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG).
